#: materiel-identity.rst:1
msgid "Materiel"
msgstr ""

#: materiel-identity.rst:6
msgid "This is a draft claim field set currently in development. The format described in this documentation is a proposed format which may change with further research and development."
msgstr ""

#: materiel-identity.rst:8
msgid "The :ref:`materiel` claim type describes basic identifying information about :ref:`materiel`: name, aliases, classifications, and associated time ranges with them. Claims of this type are grouped together with :ref:`equipment` which links a :ref:`unit` to the :ref:`materiel` it uses. :ref:`component` captures how :ref:`materiel` may include other :ref:`materiel`, for example the targeting system in a particular type of aircraft."
msgstr ""

