#: materiel-identity.rst:374
msgid "We use classifications to describe the basic nature of specific materiel to assist investigations of potential linkages between reports of human rights abuses and the Security Force Monitor’s dataset."
msgstr ""

#: materiel-identity.rst:377
msgid "materiel:media_description:annotation"
msgstr ""

#: materiel-identity.rst:383
msgid "Short textual description of material found in a media resource that provides information about how the materiel looks or sounds."
msgstr ""

#: materiel-identity.rst:403
msgid "``side of aircraft``"
msgstr ""

#: materiel-identity.rst:408
msgid "This attribute is used to store a brief description of the content of external media. The description should be sufficient for the analyst to quickly appraise what they can expect to find in the media about what the person looks or sounds like. A new row is created for each distinct media item about the materiel."
msgstr ""

